Quais recursos serão utilizados:

Compute - VMs/instances para microservices (k8s nodes) ou Fargate; serverless para funções.
Storage - Object Storage (S3), block storage para DB (EBS), snapshots.
Database - RDS (primary + read replicas), NoSQL (DynamoDB).
Networking - Load Balancers, NAT gateways, VPC endpoints.
CDN - edge for assets & game binaries.
Message queue / streaming - Kafka / Kinesis / PubSub.
Monitoring/logging - Managed monitoring, logs ingestion, retention costs.
Security - WAF, KMS keys, Secrets Manager.
Backups - snapshot storage and lifecycle.
Bandwidth (egress) | importante para jogos/patches - principal custo variável.
